---
import Base from "../layouts/base.astro";
---

<Base title="Clarity. — What is Insight-as-a-Service?">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 text-center">
    <!-- Heading sits visually above the box -->
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">
      What is Insight-as-a-Service?
    </h1>

    <!-- Insight-as-a-Service Explainer -->
    <section
      class="mt-[1rem] bg-gray-900 text-white py-16 px-6 rounded-lg text-center"
    >
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        You're under pressure to decide. Fast.<br />
        But alignment is messy, data is patchy.<br />
        You can't leverage support at the speed you need it.<br />
        <br />
      </p>

      <p class="text-xl font-semibold">
        That's why we created Insight-as-a-Service — a model designed to meet
        you in motion.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Insight Grid -->
    <section class="mt-20 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-left">
      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-center mb-2">Strategic Access.</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
          Structured thinking, not scoped outputs.<br />
          Insight, facilitation, and decision support — on repeat.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-center mb-2">Built for Pace.</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
          You don't stop moving, and neither do we.<br />
          Each cycle builds on the last. No resets.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-center mb-2">
          Tangible Outcomes.
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
          Every session produces momentum.<br />
          You leave with clarity, not a cloud of opinions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-black/20 shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-center mb-2">
          Context that Compounds.
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-center">
          No rebriefs. No need to explain things twice.<br />
          We retain insight and build on it — just like a great team member would.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Navigation Arrows -->
    <section class="my-32 flex justify-center items-center gap-16">
      <!-- Left Arrow Link -->
      <a
        href="/why-clarity"
        aria-label="Previous page"
        class="hover:text-blue-600 transition"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          width="64"
          height="64"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>

      <!-- Right Arrow Link -->
      <a
        href="/why-insight-as-a-service"
        aria-label="Next page"
        class="hover:text-blue-600 transition"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          width="64"
          height="64"
        >
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section
      id="final-cta"
      class="mt-20 bg-gray-900 text-white py-12 px-6 rounded-lg text-center"
    >
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Feel ready?</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-lg">
        That's why Clarity exists.<br /> We give you information and insight so you
        can make great decisions. <br /><br />No fluff. No spam. Just Clarity.<br
        /><br />
      </p>
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-block bg-white text-black font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-gray-200 transition"
        >Join the Waitlist</a
      >
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
